name: 索耶·赫塞·米克松
name_full: 索耶·赫塞·米克松 Sawyer Jesse Mixon
introduction: Sawyer Jesse "SJ" Mixon recently landed a guest star role playing a young Mark-Paul Gosselar on NBC's new show, Found.His breakout role is supporting lead, Jase Robertson. He plays a son of the well known Robertson family, or more commonly known as The Duck Dynasty Family. The movie is an upcoming feature film that comes out later this year, The Blind.
